# Django API origin (no trailing slash). Default in code: http://api.shyam-sweets.com
#
# This repo ships `.env.development` → hosted API for `npm run dev`, and `.env.production` for `vite build`.
# To use a local Django server during dev instead, create `.env.development.local` (gitignored) with:
# VITE_API_BASE=http://api.shyam-sweets.com
VITE_API_BASE=http://api.shyam-sweets.com

# Optional dev-only: bypass the API and set a Google Maps JS key directly. Production loads the key from
# GET /api/google-maps-js-key/ (Django fetches it from Infelo; see server infelo-api-map.md).
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
